column16: Josh Donaldson singles on a ground ball to right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall.   Darwin Barney scores.    Ezequiel Carrera to 2nd.
Ezequiel Carrera singles on a ground ball to right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall, deflected by first baseman Carlos Santana.   Junior Lake scores.    Darwin Barney to 3rd.
Darwin Barney singles on a line drive to right fielder Lonnie Chisenhall.   Junior Lake to 2nd.
Justin Smoak grounds out, shortstop Francisco Lindor to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Troy Tulowitzki homers (14) on a fly ball to left field.   Michael Saunders scores.    Russell Martin scores.
Russell Martin walks.   Michael Saunders to 2nd.
Michael Saunders called out on strikes.
Tom Gorzelanny intentionally walks Lorenzo Cain.
Eric Hosmer grounds out sharply, second baseman Jason Kipnis to shortstop Francisco Lindor to first baseman Mike Napoli.   Drew Butera scores.    Whit Merrifield to 3rd.    Alcides Escobar to 2nd.
Kole Calhoun grounds out softly to first baseman Carlos Santana.
Seth Smith called out on strikes.
Norichika Aoki lines out to center fielder Rajai Davis.
Jared Hoying pops out to first baseman Carlos Santana in foul territory.
